âœ… This makes sure that attribute-based routes are processed correctly.

7. If All Else Fails â€” Debug at the Network Layer
ðŸ‘‰ If the remote call still isnâ€™t happening:

Open Chrome DevTools â†’ Network tab

Filter by XHR or Fetch

Type a value â†’ Look for a GET request to ValidateWidgetData

If nothing appears:

The data-val attributes are missing (model binding issue).

The request is being blocked (possibly CORS or route issue).
